# Ent kit dev (multi-root)

| Folder | Role |
|--------|------|
| **ent-kit** | Product source — manifest, CLI, adapters |
| **Ent-workspace-test** | Consumer fixture — full preload rules, MCP, `.env`, `.ent/` |

**Start here for consumer work** — audit, onboard, MCP. Kit edits happen in **ent-kit**; sync refreshes this folder.

```bash
node ent/tools/ent.mjs sync --workspace-root ../Ent-workspace-test --agent cursor
node ent/tools/ent.mjs audit --workspace-root ../Ent-workspace-test
```

Hooks on ent-kit still run for session snapshot; invariants live on **Ent-workspace-test**.
